OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1779966177
OL,3,CForty firefighters tackle field fire
OL,4,Cin scorching conditions
OL,6,FMore than 40 firefighters were called
OL,7,Fto the scene of a field fire in
OL,8,FHavant, Hampshire on Wednesday
OL,9,Fafternoon.
OL,11,FIt started on Southleigh Road shortly
OL,12,Fafter two o'clock, with initial
OL,13,Freports indicating a fire involving
OL,14,Fhay bales.
OL,16,FCrews from Havant, Cosham, Southsea
OL,17,Fand Waterlooville were supported by
OL,18,Fspecialist vehicles from Fareham,
OL,19,FPortchester and Bordon.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
