OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1779966177
OL,3,CForty firefighters tackle field fire
OL,4,Cin scorching conditions
OL,6,FFirefighters using jets, hose reels
OL,7,Fand beaters were able to surround and
OL,8,Fstop the fire which affected an area
OL,9,Fapproximately 300m by 200m in size.
OL,11,FThey managed to put the fire out and
OL,12,Fcrews remained on the scene into the
OL,13,Fnight dampening down.
OL,15,FIt follows a heatwave that has seen
OL,16,Frecord temperatures set for the month
OL,17,Fof May in recent days.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
