OL,3,CForty firefighters tackle field fire
OL,4,Cin scorching conditions
OL,6,FHampshire @Isle of Wight Fire & Rescue
OL,7,FService warns that there is a greater
OL,8,Frisk of wildfires during hot and dry
OL,9,Fweather.
OL,11,FThey're reminding people to help
OL,12,Fprotect the countryside by leaving
OL,13,Fbarbecues at home, extinguishing
OL,14,Fcigarettes properly and not starting
OL,15,Fcampfires.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
